 arcade Beat \u2018Em Up.\nUnique Possession gameplay mechanic.\nMore than 10 Viking Clans to discover and unlock.\nEach of the 7 Viking Classes comes with unique play styles and combos.\nOver 80 skills to choose from when leveling up your Valkyrie.\nCute but bloodthirsty creatures will become your companions.\nPlay against your friends in Deathmatch and Survival modes.\nAnd more!", "themes": [{"id": 1, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 17, "name": "Fantasy"}], "url": "https://www.igdb.com/games/die-for-valhalla--1", "videos": [{"id": 20164, "name": "Trailer", "video_id": "ylIjo-qiK2Q", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ylIjo-qiK2Q", "title": "Die for Valhalla! - beat 'em up arcade adventure", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ylIjo-qiK2Q/maxresdefault.jpg"}, {"id": 20163, "name": "Trailer", "video_id": "q_hBn2Y-MHY", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q_hBn2Y-MHY", "title": "Die For Valhalla! - Switch Announcement Trailer", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/q_hBn2Y-MHY/maxresdefault.jpg"}, {"id": 20166, "name": "Trailer", "video_id": "o8e4akffVes", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o8e4akffVes", "title": "Die for Valhalla! - Xbox Announcement Trailer", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/o8e4akffVes/maxresdefault.jpg"}, {"id": 20165, "name": "Trailer", "video_id": "Avm0i47eufs", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Avm0i47eufs", "title": "Die for Valhalla! \u2013 Release Date Trailer | PS4", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Avm0i47eufs/maxresdefault.jpg"}]}